# OS
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
# NTFS "mark of the web" alternate-data-stream files. Git records the ADS colon
# as U+F03A (not ASCII ':'), so match on the suffix without the colon.
*Zone.Identifier

# Certificates (never commit private keys)
*.pfx
*.pvk
*.cer
